for single-locus data21 (Table 1). The estimations of the admixture |XML| xmlLoc_6 xmlBold_no xmlItalic_no xmlFontSize_common xmlPic_no xmlTable_no xmlBullet_no bi_xmlSFBIA_continue bi_xmlPara_continue
