1; MRH: 0.82 ± 0.12, range from 0.61 to 0.97) (see refs 20 and 19 for |XML| xmlLoc_7 xmlBold_no xmlItalic_no xmlFontSize_common xmlPic_no xmlTable_no xmlBullet_no bi_xmlSFBIA_continue bi_xmlPara_continue
